## 4. DynamoDB 스키마 설계

### 4-1. Message 테이블

| 속성 | 타입 | 역할 | 비고 |
|------|------|------|------|
| `roomId` | String (PK) | 파티션 키 | chat_rooms.id |
| `messageId` | String (SK) | 정렬 키 | ULID (시간순 정렬) |
| `senderId` | String | 발신자 | users.id |
| `messageType` | String | TEXT / AUDIO / IMAGE | |
| `content` | String | 텍스트 내용 | nullable |
| `audioUrl` | String | 음성 메시지 URL | nullable |
| `isDeleted` | Boolean | 소프트 삭제 | default false |
| `readAt` | String | 읽은 시각 (상대방) | nullable, ISO-8601 |
| `createdAt` | String | 생성 시각 | ISO-8601 |

GSI: `senderId-createdAt-index` (발신자별 메시지 조회)

### 4-2. CallEvent 테이블 (통화 이벤트 로그)

| 속성 | 타입 | 역할 |
|------|------|------|
| `callId` | String (PK) | 파티션 키 |
| `eventTime` | String (SK) | 정렬 키, ULID |
| `eventType` | String | RING / ACCEPT / DECLINE / START / END / MUTE |
| `actorId` | String | 이벤트 발생 주체 userId |
| `metadata` | Map | 추가 메타데이터 |

---

## 5. Redis 데이터 구조

### 5-1. 온라인 상태

```
SET user:online:{userId}  "1"  EX 30          # 30초 TTL, heartbeat 갱신
ZSET online_users_by_gender:{gender}  score=timestamp  member=userId
```

### 5-2. 매칭 대기 큐

```
ZSET match_queue:{gender}:{ageGroup}  score=timestamp  member=userId
# 예: match_queue:M:20s  score=1709000000  member="user-uuid"
```

### 5-3. 통화 세션

```
HASH call:session:{callId}
  callerId   → "user-uuid-1"
  calleeId   → "user-uuid-2"
  rtcRoomId  → "agora-room-id"
  status     → "ONGOING"
  startedAt  → "2026-03-03T10:00:00Z"
EX 3600                                        # 1시간 TTL
```

### 5-4. 채팅 읽지 않은 메시지 수

```
HASH unread:{userId}
  {roomId}  → count (Int)
```

---

## 6. GraphQL 스키마

파일 위치: `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/`

### schema.graphqls (루트 타입)

```graphql
type Query
type Mutation
type Subscription
```

### user.graphqls

```graphql
type User {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    gender: Int!
    birthDate: String!
    mannerScore: Int!
    status: Int!
    countryCode: String
    profile: Profile
    createdAt: String!
}

type Profile {
    id: ID!
    userId: ID!
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    voiceSampleUrls: [String!]!
    height: Int!
    job: String
    region: String
    interests: [String!]!
    isProfilePublic: Boolean!
}

type SimpleUser {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    gender: Int!
    profileImageUrl: String
    mannerScore: Int!
}

input UpdateProfileInput {
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    voiceSampleUrls: [String!]
    height: Int
    job: String
    region: String
    interests: [String!]
    isProfilePublic: Boolean
}

extend type Query {
    me: User!
    user(userId: ID!): User
    users(limit: Int, offset: Int): [User!]!
}

extend type Mutation {
    updateProfile(input: UpdateProfileInput!): Profile!
    deleteAccount: Boolean!
}
```

### match.graphqls

```graphql
type Match {
    id: ID!
    requester: SimpleUser!
    receiver: SimpleUser!
    status: MatchStatus!
    respondedAt: String
    expiredAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

enum MatchStatus {
    PENDING
    ACCEPTED
    REJECTED
    EXPIRED
}

input CreateMatchInput {
    receiverId: ID!
}

extend type Query {
    myMatches(status: MatchStatus, limit: Int, offset: Int): [Match!]!
    match(matchId: ID!): Match
}

extend type Mutation {
    createMatch(input: CreateMatchInput!): Match!
    respondMatch(matchId: ID!, accept: Boolean!): Match!
}
```

### call.graphqls

```graphql
type Call {
    id: ID!
    caller: SimpleUser!
    callee: SimpleUser!
    status: CallStatus!
    callType: CallType!
    durationSeconds: Int!
    startedAt: String
    endedAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

enum CallStatus {
    RINGING
    ONGOING
    ENDED
    MISSED
    DECLINED
}

enum CallType {
    VOICE
    VIDEO
}

type CallSession {
    callId: ID!
    rtcRoomId: String!
    token: String!
}

input InitiateCallInput {
    calleeId: ID!
    callType: CallType!
}

extend type Query {
    myCallHistory(limit: Int, offset: Int): [Call!]!
    call(callId: ID!): Call
}

extend type Mutation {
    initiateCall(input: InitiateCallInput!): CallSession!
    respondCall(callId: ID!, accept: Boolean!): CallSession
    endCall(callId: ID!): Call!
}
```

### chat.graphqls

```graphql
type ChatRoom {
    id: ID!
    matchId: ID!
    partner: SimpleUser!
    status: String!
    lastMessageAt: String
    lastMessagePreview: String
    unreadCount: Int!
}

type Message {
    messageId: ID!
    roomId: ID!
    sender: SimpleUser!
    messageType: MessageType!
    content: String
    audioUrl: String
    isDeleted: Boolean!
    readAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

enum MessageType {
    TEXT
    AUDIO
    IMAGE
}

input SendMessageInput {
    roomId: ID!
    messageType: MessageType!
    content: String
    audioUrl: String
}

extend type Query {
    myChatRooms(limit: Int, offset: Int): [ChatRoom!]!
    messages(roomId: ID!, limit: Int, lastMessageId: String): [Message!]!
}

extend type Mutation {
    sendMessage(input: SendMessageInput!): Message!
    markAsRead(roomId: ID!, messageId: ID!): Boolean!
    leaveChatRoom(roomId: ID!): Boolean!
}

extend type Subscription {
    messageReceived(roomId: ID!): Message!
}
```

